BEGIN_PGML
Prove that [`\renewcommand{\v}{\vtx{above}{}}\newcommand{\lt}{<}2^n \lt n!`] for all [`n \ge 4\text{.}`] (Recall, [`n! = 1\cdot 2 \cdot 3 \cdot \cdots\cdot n\text{.}`])

